Year Ended December 31, 2017 Compared to Year Ended December 31, 2016
Service fee revenue. Service fee revenue increased $7.4 million, or 3.3%, in 2017 as compared to 2016. The increase in service fee revenue in 2017 as compared to 2016 was primarily due to the impact of expanded and new client relationships, partially offset by the conclusion or reduction of operations of certain client programs during 2017.
